Interpretation: Perfect-Isomorphism.md and Allomorphs.md make this a family-selection check, not a decode. The observed 0 robust strong-bar internal violations SUPPORTS (does not prove) perfect isomorphism and keeps the GAK family viable; it does not imply "the eyes are GAK." A clean internal violation would disfavor the proven CTAK..XGAK family, but XGAK's upper edge is <=, not equality.
